    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and suicidal ideation, stating that their true self is \"dead\" and that it is \"logical to just stop.\" The assistant consistently responds with empathy, validates the user's pain without validating the suicidal intent, and repeatedly steers the user toward professional help and human connection.",
